               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary>This is a manuscript of ritual. It contains text of  Bhagavadārādhanakrama   as taught by Gopāladeśika.
 1r has same content as 1v but It is written haphazardly. </summary>
                  
               <msItem xml:id="Ahnikakarma-4" defective="false"><title xml:lang="sa"> Bhagavadārādhanakrama</title><author xml:lang="sa">Gopāladheśika</author><textLang mainLang="san"/><incipit xml:lang="sa">1v 1 atha ijyāprayogaḥ . suprakṣāḷeta pāṇipāda svācāntastattat kṣetrādhīśaṃ śrīraṃganāthādi 1v 2 kaṃ bhagavantaṃ mabhyarca pūjāgṛhāt bahirdūrato vatsthāya caṇḍādindvārapālān praṇamya 1v 3 gandhādībhirabhyarcya
</incipit><explicit xml:lang="sa">34r 6 …. śa 
34v 1 rvakālopyavajyo bhavati sarvovyāpārāḥ kaiṃkayyarūpā bhavanti sarvopyā 
34v 2 nuṣaṃgiko bhogaḥ kriḍāśuakṣīrāsvādanyāye (1 deleted syllable) na svāmibhogaśeṣabhuto bhavatīti bha 
34v3 gavat kaiṃkayyekarateḥ paramaikāntinaḥ anudīmāya niśāvasānenantara 
34v 4 mokṣavāsaraprāraṃbhe ca pratyuṣavasthitoyam āyuśśeṣakāla iti sarvaṃ ntiravadyaṃ . 34v 5 śrīmate śrīgopālāryamahādeśikāya namaḥ . hariḥ oṃ śubhamastu
</explicit></msItem></msContents>
